            <p><add hand="#barker">Marriage permit&#8212; Betsey Bright to Noel Roberts.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            
<p>Be it Known that we <persName>David Bright</persName> and <persName>Judy Bright</persName> the <persName>Parents
of Betsey Bright</persName> do hereby  agree that our said <persName>Daughter </persName>may
Marry <persName>Noel Roberts</persName>&#8212;   witness our hands <date when="1824-05-10">May 10, 1824</date>
<placeName>Bracis River, Prove of Texas</placeName></p>

<p><persName>David Bright</persName></p>
<p>for himself and for his <persName>wife </persName><persName>Judy Bright</persName>
Attest    <persName>S. F. Austin Judge</persName></p>

        </div1>
